OL,3,CCruise employee admits hiding cameras
OL,4,Cand filming guest's in their bathrooms
OL,6,FA 34-year-old Royal Caribbean cruise
OL,7,Femployee has been accused of hiding
OL,8,Fcameras inside bathrooms of passenger
OL,9,Fcabins to spy on guests.
OL,11,FArvin Joseph Mirasol was arrested on
OL,12,FSunday on federal charges of
OL,13,Fproduction and possession of child
OL,14,Fpornography after the Symphony of the
OL,15,FSeas ship arrived in Fort Lauderdale,
OL,16,FFlorida, according to a case filed in
OL,17,Fthe US District Court of .
OL,19,FHe also faces six counts of voyeurism
OL,20,Fin state court.
