OL,6,FA guest staying in a cabin, where
OL,7,FMirasol was an attendant, found a
OL,8,Fcamera in the bathroom on February 25.
OL,9,FIt was "affixed to the counter
OL,10,Funderneath the sink," according to the
OL,11,Faffidavit.
OL,13,FShe reported the incident to ship
OL,14,Fofficials, who sent security to the
OL,15,Froom to investigate.
OL,17,FMirasol, who is from the Philippines,
OL,18,Fwas detained on the until March 3,
OL,19,Fwhen it docked in Fort Lauderdale.
