OL,6,FHe was questioned by agents from
OL,7,FHomeland Security, Customs and Border
OL,8,FProtection and the Broward Sheriff's
OL,9,FOffice.
OL,11,FAgents discovered "numerous videos of
OL,12,Fnaked females" as well as images of
OL,13,Fchild sexual abuse while looking at
OL,14,Fhis phone, an SD card and USB stick,
OL,15,Fthe affidavit said.
OL,17,FOne of the videos showed Mirasol
OL,18,Finstalling a camera in a guest cabin's
OL,19,Fbathroom.
