OL,6,FIn one five-minute video, a 10-year-
OL,7,Fold girl entered the bathroom, removed
OL,8,Fher clothes and got into the shower,
OL,9,Fthe affidavit said.
OL,11,FMirasol told investigators he had been
OL,12,Fplacing cameras in bathrooms since he
OL,13,Fbegan working on the ship in December.
OL,15,F"I want to control it, but I can't,"
OL,16,Fhe told investigators.
OL,18,FHe admitted he knew it was illegal to .
OL,20,FAgents asked him how he chose where to
OL,21,Fput the cameras.
